        "question_NLXwMW": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question_header": "What is Mystery Tackle Box?",
            "question_text": "<p>Mystery Tackle Box is a fun and affordable way to discover new fishing products every single month! Our subscription plans introduce beginner and expert anglers alike to new fishing lures and tackle, and the best way to use them.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_Fr4feH": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question_header": "How Much Does it Cost?",
            "question_text": "<p>Mystery Tackle Box is only $19.99 a month for our regular box, $31.99 a month for our PRO box, and $44.99 for our Elite box (plus any applicable shipping and tax). You can cancel or change species any time! Most anglers spend at least $25-$50 per month on fishing gear, so our service exposes anglers to new quality lures at a fraction of the price.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_mc9q3B": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question_header": "What Will I Get?",
            "question_text": "<p>Each month you will get a variety of quality fishing tackle from both large and small manufacturers. We curate a unique mix of brands and product types in each box so you can discover new tackle and techniques every single month. Our team of seasoned tournament anglers meticulously assess each bait we send to ensure your greatest chance of success and satisfaction on the water.</p>"
          }
        },
        "question_Y7zMNh": {
          "type": "question",
          "settings": {
            "question_header": "How Do I Cancel?",
            "question_text": "<p>If you decide you no longer want to receive a Mystery Tackle Box each month you can easily cancel by logging into your account. From there you will see all your active subscriptions. You can scroll to the bottom and select to pause your subscription for a selected number of months or stop it completely.</p><p></p><p>*Please note that when you stop your subscription, you won't be billed anything further although you will still receive the boxes you've paid for in your last order.</p>"
          }
        }
      },
